HEADWORD: Zymology
<hw>Zy*mol"o*gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Zyme</ets> +
<ets>-logy</ets>: cf. F. <ets>zymologie</ets>.]</ety> <def>A treatise on
the fermentation of liquors, or the doctrine of fermentation.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>zumology</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
